BRIEFING:
MODERATE TO BREEZY EASTERLY TRADES WILL CONTINUE THROUGH MONDAY. PASSING CLOUDS AND BRIEF SHOWERS WILL FAVOR WINDWARD AND MOUNTAIN SLOPES DURING THE OVERNIGHT TO EARLY MORNING HOURS.
AIRMET TANGO FOR LOW-LEVEL TURBULENCE DOWNSTREAM OF ISLAND TERRAIN IS LIKELY BY MONDAY AFTERNOON DUE TO THE STRENGTHENING TRADE WINDS.
